  <note line="86" original="na sampassati (sī.)" reference-line="38" id="11">
    <extra></extra>
    <alternatives>
      <alternative source-abbr="vri" source="vipassana research institut">na samanupassati</alternative>
      <alternative source-abbr="sī." source="sri lanka">na sampassati</alternative>
    </alternatives>
    <type>auto</type>
    <previous>Kasmā ca, bhikkhave, assaddhassa saddhākathā dukkathā? Assaddho, bhikkhave, saddhākathāya kacchamānāya abhisajjati kuppati byāpajjati patitthīyati kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti. Taṃ kissa hetu? Tañhi so, bhikkhave, saddhāsampadaṃ attani na samanupassati </previous>
  </note>
